title: Osibisa-Woyaya
description:
Woyaya is Osibisa&#039;s second album also recorded in 1971 and recorded at Air Studios, London UK.  This recording has been touted as a live album, yet it is a studio recording in a group format. This acounts for the background sounds and voices.  The file is in wma format.  Includes cover and inner sleeve photos.
